Deployment
==========

Standardize directories, configs, scripts

Fat tarballs for self-contained installation, all the files needed and dependencies may live outside

Chef
  deploy via erlang_apps
  Simply chef API for deploying erlang releases
  https://github.com/fastip/fastip_cookbooks
  Joe wrote support for erl_call


Continuous Integration
  * publish tarballs to CI system
  * rebar can publish code upgrades


Hot Upgrades
  * generate appup files via rebar
  * generate upgrade tarballs via rebar
  * all of this can be done via CI
